《'''以色列與阿拉伯聯合大公國和平協議'''》（{{lang-en|Israel–United Arab Emirates peace treaty}}），简称《'''以阿和平协议'''》，或稱《'''亞伯拉罕協定'''》（{{lang-en|Abraham Accords}}）<ref name=Reuters>{{cite news|title=With Trump's help, Israel and the United Arab Emirates reach historic deal to normalize relations|url=https://www.reuters.com/article/us-israel-emirates-trump/with-trumps-help-israel-and-the-united-arab-emirates-reach-historic-deal-to-normalize-relations-idUSKCN25926W|first=Steve|last=Holland|date=2020-08-13|accessdate=2020-08-13|agency=Reuters|archive-date=2020-08-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200813152145/https://www.reuters.com/article/us-israel-emirates-trump/with-trumps-help-israel-and-the-united-arab-emirates-reach-historic-deal-to-normalize-relations-idUSKCN25926W|dead-url=no}}</ref>，是由[[以色列|以色列]]和[[阿拉伯聯合大公國|阿拉伯聯合大公國]]於2020年8月13日達成。如果簽署了協議，阿拉伯聯合大公國將會是繼[[埃及|埃及]]（1979年）和[[約旦|約旦]]（1994年）之後的第三個與以色列<ref name="auto">{{Cite web|title=Israel and United Arab Emirates Strike Major Diplomatic Agreement|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2020/08/13/us/politics/trump-israel-united-arab-emirates-uae.html|accessdate=|author=|date=2020-08-13|format=|publisher=|language=|first1=Peter|last1=Baker|first2=Isabel|last2=Kershner|first3=David D.|last3=Kirkpatrick|website=New York Times|archive-date=2020-08-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200813152005/https://www.nytimes.com/2020/08/13/us/politics/trump-israel-united-arab-emirates-uae.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=Reuters/><ref name=Smith>{{cite news|title=Israel, United Arab Emirates agree full normalization of relations|url=https://www.nbcnews.com/news/world/israel-united-arab-emirates-agree-full-normalization-relations-n1236606|first=Saphora|last=Smith|date=2020-08-13|accessdate=2020-08-13|website=NBC News|archive-date=2020-08-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200813171216/https://www.nbcnews.com/news/world/israel-united-arab-emirates-agree-full-normalization-relations-n1236606|dead-url=no}}</ref>簽署和平協議的[[阿拉伯國家|阿拉伯國家]]，以及第一個簽署該協議的[[波斯灣國家|波斯灣國家]]。<ref name=AJ1>{{cite news|title=Israel and UAE announce normalisation of relations with US help|url=https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2020/08/israel-uae-announce-normalisation-relations-200813145645861.html|date=2020-08-13|accessdate=2020-08-13|publisher=Al Jazeera|archive-date=2020-08-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200813165717/https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2020/08/israel-uae-announce-normalisation-relations-200813145645861.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=BBC>{{cite news|title=Israel and UAE strike historic deal to normalise relations|url=https://www.bbc.com/news/world-middle-east-53770859|date=August  13, 2020|accessdate=2020-08-13|website=BBC News|archive-date=2020-08-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200813152232/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-middle-east-53770859|dead-url=no}}</ref>該條約將解決两国之間的緊張[[以色列－阿联酋关系|关系]]。同時，以色列同意暫時中止[[吞併約旦河谷|吞併約旦河谷]]的計劃。<ref name="AJ1" /><ref>{{cite news|title=Israel and United Arab Emirates strike historic peace accord|url=https://www.ft.com/content/2712a625-e2d4-41f3-9ef1-536d0700cbb8|publisher=FT|date=2020-08-13|access-date=2020-08-13|archive-date=2020-08-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200813171226/https://www.ft.com/content/2712a625-e2d4-41f3-9ef1-536d0700cbb8|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==背景==
早在1971年，阿拉伯聯合大公國第一任總統[[扎耶德·本·蘇爾坦·阿勒納哈揚|扎耶德·本·蘇爾坦·阿勒納哈揚]]就曾將以色列稱為“敵人”<ref>{{cite web |author=Kristian Coates Ulrichsen |url=https://www.bakerinstitute.org/media/files/research_document/13eaaa71/CME-pub-GCCIsrael-090716.pdf |title=Israel and the Arab Gulf States: Drivers and Directions of Change |publisher=Rice University's Baker Institute for Public Policy |page=3 |date=September 2016 |accessdate=2020-08-14 |archive-date=2016-09-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160909234012/https://www.bakerinstitute.org/media/files/research_document/13eaaa71/CME-pub-GCCIsrael-090716.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2015年11月，以色列宣布他們將在阿拉伯聯合大公國開設外交辦事處，這是十多年來以色列首次在波斯灣國家中正式派駐人員。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Israel to Open Diplomatic Office in United Arab Emirates|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2015/11/28/world/middleeast/israel-to-open-diplomatic-office-in-united-arab-emirates.html|accessdate=|author=|date=2015-11-27|last=Hadid|first=Diaa|format=|publisher=|language=|website=The New York Times|archive-date=2015-11-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151127220419/https://www.nytimes.com/2015/11/28/world/middleeast/israel-to-open-diplomatic-office-in-united-arab-emirates.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>2019年8月，在與[[伊朗|伊朗]]的緊張局勢加劇的情況下，以色列外交部長就與阿拉伯聯合大公國的軍事合作發表了公開聲明。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://breakingdefense.com/2019/08/israel-meets-with-uae-declares-its-joining-persian-gulf-coalition/|title=Israel Meets with UAE, Declares It's Joining Persian Gulf Coalition|first=Sydney J., Jr.|last=Freedberg|accessdate=2020-08-14|archive-date=2019-08-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190816212630/https://breakingdefense.com/2019/08/israel-meets-with-uae-declares-its-joining-persian-gulf-coalition/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

在達成該協議的前幾個月中，以色列一直在與阿拉伯聯合大公國秘密合作以對抗[[COVID-19|COVID-19]]大流行。歐洲新聞媒體報導說，[[以色列情報及特殊使命局|以色列情報及特殊使命局]]謹慎地從波斯灣國家那裡獲得了醫療設備。<ref>{{cite web|title=Israel and United Arab Emirates Strike Major Diplomatic Agreement|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2020/08/13/us/politics/trump-israel-united-arab-emirates-uae.html|accessdate=2020-08-13|author=|date=2020-08-13|format=|publisher=|language=|first1=Peter|last1=Baker|first2=Isabel|last2=Kershner|first3=David D.|last3=Kirkpatrick|newspaper=The New York Times|archive-date=2020-08-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200813152005/https://www.nytimes.com/2020/08/13/us/politics/trump-israel-united-arab-emirates-uae.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Israel’s Not-So-Secret Weapon in Coronavirus Fight: The Spies of Mossad|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2020/04/12/world/middleeast/coronavirus-israel-mossad.html|accessdate=|author=|date=2020-04-12|last=Bergman|first=Ronen|format=|publisher=|language=|website=The New York Times|archive-date=2020-04-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200412204005/https://www.nytimes.com/2020/04/12/world/middleeast/coronavirus-israel-mossad.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>[[以色列總理|以色列總理]][[班傑明·納坦雅胡|班傑明·納坦雅胡]]在2020年6月底報告說，兩國正在合作抗擊冠狀病毒，而摩薩德首領[[尤西·科恩|尤西·科恩]]（Yossi Cohen）曾多次前往阿聯酋。但是，幾個小時後，阿聯酋似乎對此不屑一顧，因為它表明這只是私人的行程安排，而非國際間的交流。<ref>{{cite web|title=Israel Announces Partnership with U.A.E., Which Throws Cold Water On It|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2020/06/25/world/middleeast/israel-united-arab-emirates-coronavirus.html|accessdate=2020-08-13|author=|date=2020-06-25|format=|publisher=|language=|first1=Ronen|last1=Bergman|first2=Ben|last2=Hubbard|newspaper=The New York Times|archive-date=2020-06-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200625160029/https://www.nytimes.com/2020/06/25/world/middleeast/israel-united-arab-emirates-coronavirus.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

川普政府終止[[伊朗核協議|伊朗核協議]]後，以色列對伊朗發展[[伊朗核計劃|伊朗核計劃]]的擔憂加劇，[[德黑蘭|德黑蘭]]否認了這一舉動。目前，伊朗在從[[敘利亞|敘利亞]]到[[葉門|葉門]]的[[代理戰爭|代理戰爭]]中支持不同派系，阿拉伯聯合大公國支持[[沙烏地阿拉伯|沙烏地阿拉伯]]領導的聯軍打擊在該地區作戰的伊朗結盟部隊。<ref name=":0" />近年來，因為這些外部因素，這些國家的非正式關係大大升溫，並基於對伊朗核計劃和地區影響的共同反對，進行了廣泛的非正式合作。<ref name="newyorker">''The New Yorker'', 16 June 2018, [https://www.newyorker.com/magazine/2018/06/18/donald-trumps-new-world-order "Donald Trump's New World Order"] {{Wayback|url=https://www.newyorker.com/magazine/2018/06/18/donald-trumps-new-world-order |date=20180611112529 }}</ref> 

該協議也被正式稱為“亞伯拉罕協議”，以紀念[[亞伯拉罕|亞伯拉罕]]，世界上三種主要[[亞伯拉罕宗教|亞伯拉罕宗教]]（[[猶太教|猶太教]]、[[伊斯蘭教|伊斯蘭教]]和[[基督教|基督教]]）的先祖。<ref>{{cite web|title=Trump Announces 'Historic Breakthrough' Between Israel, UAE|url=https://www.voanews.com/usa/trump-announces-historic-breakthrough-between-israel-uae|date=2020-08-13|accessdate=2020-08-13|publisher=[[Voice_of_America|Voice of America]]|archive-date=2020-08-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200814020742/https://www.voanews.com/usa/trump-announces-historic-breakthrough-between-israel-uae/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==協議==
[[File:President_Trump_Delivers_a_Statement_from_the_Oval_Office_01.jpg|thumb]][[橢圓形辦公室|橢圓形辦公室]]向媒體宣布了該協議]]

2020年8月13日，阿拉伯聯合大公國外交大臣[[安瓦爾·加加什|安瓦爾·加加什]]（Anwar Gargash）宣布阿拉伯聯合大公國同意與以色列實現關係正常化的協議，稱阿拉伯聯合大公國希望應對兩國解決方案所面臨的威脅，特別是吞併[[巴勒斯坦|巴勒斯坦]]領土並敦促巴勒斯坦人和以色列人返回談判桌。他表示，他認為直到巴勒斯坦人和以色列人之間達成最終協議之後，耶路撒冷才會有大使館。<ref>{{cite news|date=August 13, 2020|title=Further Israeli annexation of Palestinian territories would have eliminated hope for peace: UAE|publisher=AMN|url=https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/further-israeli-annexation-of-palestinian-territories-would-have-eliminated-hope-for-peace-uae/|access-date=August 13, 2020|archive-date=2020-08-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200813171541/https://www.almasdarnews.com/article/further-israeli-annexation-of-palestinian-territories-would-have-eliminated-hope-for-peace-uae/|dead-url=no}}</ref>[[美國總統|美國總統]][[唐納·川普|川普]]和[[以色列總理|以色列總理]][[班傑明·納坦雅胡|班傑明·納坦雅胡]]說：「以色列和阿拉伯聯合大公國將使兩國關係全面正常化」。他們將互設使館和大使，並開始在包括旅遊，教育，保健，貿易和安全在內的廣泛領域進行全面合作。”<ref>{{Cite web|last=News|first=A. B. C.|title=Israel, UAE agree to normalize ties in what Trump calls a 'historic' agreement|url=https://abcnews.go.com/International/president-trump-historic-peace-agreement-made-israel-uae/story?id=72350077|access-date=2020-08-13|website=ABC News|language=en|archive-date=2020-08-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200813151621/https://abcnews.go.com/International/president-trump-historic-peace-agreement-made-israel-uae/story?id=72350077|dead-url=no}}</ref>

川普、納坦雅胡和扎耶德發表的聯合聲明中寫道：“這一歷史性外交突破將促進[[中東|中東]]地區的和平，這證明了三位領導人的大膽外交和遠見以及阿拉伯聯合大公國和以色列的勇氣繪製一條新的道路，將釋放該地區的巨大潛力。”<ref name=":0">{{Cite news|date=2020-08-13|title=Israel, UAE agree to normalise relations, with help from Trump|language=en|work=Reuters|url=https://www.reuters.com/article/us-israel-emirates-trump-idUSKCN25926W|access-date=2020-08-13|archive-date=2020-08-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200813221727/https://www.reuters.com/article/us-israel-emirates-trump-idUSKCN25926W/|dead-url=no}}</ref>阿拉伯聯合大公國表示將繼續支持巴勒斯坦人民，該協議將保持以色列和巴勒斯坦之間兩國解決方案的前景。儘管達成了協議，但納坦雅胡表示，以色列對約旦河谷的主權主張仍在議程中，只是暫時凍結。<ref name=":0" />

扎耶德在推特上說：“阿拉伯聯合大公國和以色列也同意合作，並為建立雙邊關係設定了路線圖。”<ref name="auto"/>

預計和平協定將於9月初在[[白宮|白宮]]簽署。<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.france24.com/en/20200813-israel-uae-normalise-relations-in-historic-trump-brokered-deal |title=Israel, UAE normalise relations in historic, Trump-brokered deal |work=France24 |date=August 13, 2020 |accessdate=August 14, 2020 |archive-date=2020-08-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200814141646/https://www.france24.com/en/20200813-israel-uae-normalise-relations-in-historic-trump-brokered-deal |dead-url=no }}</ref>

